Ki naken, da' ẕnna x̱tiža' Dios bchi'len žo'o, na' goken chežo ka to benne' bsedle' žo'o na' zejte ža bḻoe'e ḻaw Jesús, Benne' Criston', nich gak yeyakžo chawe' ḻaw Dios cha' chejḻe'žo chie' Ḻe'.
Da' gok Agar na' ḻezka' ẕḻoe'elen kan nak ya'a Sinaí, dan' žen' gan nbab Arabia, na' ḻezka' ẕḻoe'elen kan nak yež Jerusalén dan' žen' na'a ža, dan' naken ka to benne' ndo'w tẕen ḻen benne' ka' zej nnite'e ḻo yežen'.
