Chope benne' ki nzi' ḻo ná'gake' wséjwgake' x̱nez nis yejw che ya'abá, nich bi gak yejw kate' ža ka' žaḻa' wcháḻjgake' ḻo wláz Dios, na' ḻezka' nzi' ḻo ná'gake' góngake' ga yeyák nis žen, na' góngake' ga galj yižwé' yežlyó nga, na' ki góngake' baḻe chí'iteze yénegekle'.
Ḻen x̱banba' wẕobba' to kwe' che chonne kwe' belj ka' zej nḻa' ya'abá, na' bžo'nba' ḻégaken ḻo yežlyó. Wzé bele ẕen sniaḻe'e na' ḻaw no'len' ba žalj x̱kwide' chie', na' wzoaba' gawba' x̱kwide' chien' kate' ba naljbe'.
Wzó ḻawba' ẕnneba' che Dios, na' wnné zi'ba' che La Dios, na' che latje la'y chie', na' chegak benne' ka' nníta'gake' ya'abá che Dios.
Dios wsaka' zi'e ḻe' ḻo yeḻa' ẕža'a chie'. Sáka'ḻe'e bennen' ḻo yi', na' ḻo dan' ẕzeyḻe'en, ḻawgak wbás che ya'abá ka', na' ḻaw Bennen' nake' Ẕíla'do'.
